                <div class="col-span-2 backdrop-blur-md p-2">
                    <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-10">Evolution</h2>
                    <p>
                        The application has evolved significantly from its
                        previous version. It was completely rewritten using the
                        latest version of React Native, and based on previous
                        experience, the design was optimized.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        This update allowed for the addition of new features,
                        improved performance, and enhanced the development
                        experience. As a result, the application is faster and
                        more efficient, providing a better user experience in
                        all areas.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Over time, the need arose to store copies of important
                        documents, such as vehicle maintenance records, more
                        efficiently. This included the ability to attach photos
                        to visually document each maintenance event, eliminating
                        the reliance on handwritten notes or scattered Excel
                        files. In response, a special section was implemented in
                        SCPP that allows users to upload photos with dates and
                        descriptions. This simplifies document management by
                        centralizing them, making them easier to access, and
                        providing a comprehensive solution for tracking and
                        recording relevant activities.
                    </p>
